node.text:
This makes me soo Happy 🥲❤️

Amaya, Maysa and Layna you girls are so cool 🙌🏼🔥 I’m so proud of you and I can’t wait to meet you 🤗 ❤️❤️ until then keep shredding 🛹⚡️💃 

Thank you @bbcnews for telling this story. ❤️ 

@teamgb @olympics  @monarchproject @worldskateofficial @worldskatesb @nikesb 

#skateboard #skybrown #olympics #tokyo2020 #teamgb #teamgalaxy

node.text:
It was a dream to get a Gold at @xgames this weekend, 
I still can’t believe it’s real. 😆✨💫⚡️ 
I’m so proud of all the girls, everyone crushed it. And the level of girls skating is getting crazy!!🔥 🙌🏼🙌🏼❤️

Massive Congrats to  @leticiabufoni @gui_khury @dashawnjordan @jimmy_wilkins @liampace_ and @jamie_foy 🥳🥳

Thank you @xgames @catrainingfacility and @espn for putting on this amazing Event.

#xgames #xgamesmode #espn #skybrown #540 #kickflindy

node.text:
I know a lot of people are worried about me, but Don’t worry, I’m Okay. 👌🏼❤️🙏🏻I’m excited to come back even stronger and even tougher.  My heart wants to go so hard right now🔥I’m just waiting for my body to catch up 👊🏼Thank you everyone for sending your love, messages and supporting me.  I’m sorry to make you worry.  I’m gonna be just fine. 💫⚡️✨
#nevergiveup #doitcosyouloveit #iloveskateboarding #skybrown  #wegothis

We woke up at 5am, to have a live chat with Ash from the  @olympicchannel 
Talking olympic dreams, tiktok, buttercake 🍰 , and how me, and my brother @oceanbrown are still having fun and staying healthy in #quarantine 🦠 #covid_19 isn’t gonna stop us from playing inside 🔥 we got this guys✊🏼❤️💪🏼 @olympics 
@olympicchannel
#keepsmiling #stayhealthy #playinside #staysafe #staystrong 
#cantstopsport #wegotthis #nike #justdoit #playfortheworld #skybrown #oceanbrown #nike #olympics  #olympicchannel

I did an air over Tony Hawk ?! 🦅 🤯🙋🏼‍♀️🤩 I still can’t stop saying it to myself 😻it makes my cheeks hurt😆.
This A moment I will appreciate and treasure forever. ✊🏼❤️
Thankyou so much @tonyhawk for this experience and for supporting me, and pushing me, and most of all trusting me more than I trusted me 🙋🏼‍♀️ 🙏🏻🙏🏻🛹🛹🙌🏻🙌🏻. .
@900films 🎥 
@chrisclicksdigital 📸

#skateboardingisfun 
#tonyhawk
#skybrown

This makes me soo Happy 🥲❤️

Amaya, Maysa and Layna you girls are so cool 🙌🏼🔥 I’m so proud of you and I can’t wait to meet you 🤗 ❤️❤️ until then keep shredding 🛹⚡️💃 

Thank you @bbcnews for telling this story. ❤️ 

@teamgb @olympics  @monarchproject @worldskateofficial @worldskatesb @nikesb 

#skateboard #skybrown #olympics #tokyo2020 #teamgb #teamgalaxy

node.text:
@thvertalert was Incredible!!! 💫
I was hyped to win🥇💃 
Skating Vert with everyone was too FUN! It was really cool watching the Legends, Pros and Women destroy the Vert together.🛹🔥🔥

Thank you @tonyhawk for putting this event on, and for letting me join🙌🏼🙌🏼🙏🏻 I hope we can do it again soon. 😬🙏🏻🙏🏻😆
I wish that one day Vert skateboarding can be a part of the @olympics and the world can see it. 

I was also really happy to watch the @sls and be with some of my best friends @leticiabufoni @rayssalealsk8 and @keetoldenbeuving ❤️❤️🤗

📷 @aacostaa 

#skybrown #vertskateboading #vertalert #christair #monarchproject  #leticiabufoni #rayssaleal #tonyhawk #olympics #iloveskateboarding

node.text:
It was a dream to get a Gold at @xgames this weekend, 
I still can’t believe it’s real. 😆✨💫⚡️ 
I’m so proud of all the girls, everyone crushed it. And the level of girls skating is getting crazy!!🔥 🙌🏼🙌🏼❤️

Massive Congrats to  @leticiabufoni @gui_khury @dashawnjordan @jimmy_wilkins @liampace_ and @jamie_foy 🥳🥳

Thank you @xgames @catrainingfacility and @espn for putting on this amazing Event.

#xgames #xgamesmode #espn #skybrown #540 #kickflindy
